      <odd id="aspace_2a679de790abdc6f0b7839360474ac6a">
         <head>General note</head>
         <p>Forms part of Yale Record Group 5-B (YRG 5-B), Accounting records and records of the Yale comptroller.</p>  
      </odd>
      <acqinfo id="aspace_a4f989940ad96ce40f3ec90238a22ace">
         <head>Immediate Source of Acquisition</head>
         <p>The records were transferred from the Office of The Comptroller, 1979.</p>  
      </acqinfo>
