         <head>Preferred Citation</head>
         <p>Comptroller, Yale University, Records Concerning Patents (RU 723). Manuscripts and Archives, Yale University Library.</p>  
      </prefercite>
      <processinfo id="aspace_a82b80c57a49f2a566c7d66e3208bc52">
         <head>Processing Information</head>
         <p>Yale University records are arranged and described at the accession level by the creating office. The University Archives creates collection level descriptive records, but typically does no further arrangement and description at the accession level.</p>  
      </processinfo>
      <scopecontent id="aspace_77386c5523688b9061e9083c4cd214eb">
         <head>Scope and Contents</head>
         <p>The records consist of subject files and memoranda documenting the patent operations and activities of the Yale comptroller.</p>  
      </scopecontent>
